# Models

Trained model artifacts are not included in this repository.

## Artifacts
The following files are generated by the training pipeline but excluded from version control:
- `insider_threat_rf_model.pkl` - Random Forest classifier (selected model)
- `insider_threat_scaler.pkl` - StandardScaler fitted on training data

## Reproduce
To regenerate these artifacts, run:
- `master_training_script.py` - end-to-end pipeline in one execution
- `notebooks/` - Kaggle notebooks with fully executed outputs

All training was performed on Kaggle free CPU. No GPU required.

